Name: colarise
Version: 3.3.1
Summary: Simple package for color and formatting to terminal
Home-page: https://github.com/sudinedy/colarise/
Author: sudinedy
Author-email: sudarshan.reddy@neonage.co.in
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3
Classifier: License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License
